div.p: - The umbrella chart has dependencies on the RabbitMQ and Redis charts.
- Both sub-charts have init containers that wait for the RabbitMQ broker to come online.

When Helm installs/upgrades charts, the Kubernetes objects from the charts and all its dependencies are aggregated into a single set; then sorted by type followed by name; and then created/updated in that order.
